"glider's estimated sink rate. Best used if airspeed, accelerometers and "
"vario are connected, otherwise calculations are based on GPS measurements "
"and wind estimates."
msgstr ""
"Atnaujinta vertikala greitis, lygus vario vertė minus gliders's estimated "
"sink rate. Best used if airspeed, accelerometers and vario are connected, "
"otherwise calculations are based on GPS measurements and wind estimates."

